experiment Artemis
instrument ESR
start 2011 02 17 1900
end 2011 02 18 0100
status R
description Dayside dynamics in conjunction with Artemis spacecraft
contact L. Palin
email palin@cesr.fr
operator F. Pitout
submitter F.Pitout
resources FR(6)
notes
We plan to observe the nighside ionophere in conjunction with the Artemis
spacecraft. The following antenna will be used:
- ESR 42m + 32m pointing south at low elevation
- VHF pointing north at low elevation (split or single beam... to be defined)
- UHF pointing field aligned.
